# Normalize line endings to LF in the repo AND in every checkout, on all platforms.
# Prettier (default endOfLine "lf"), the ubuntu-only CI `format & lint` job, and the
# Windows-dev preflight (scripts/preflight.ps1, which now runs `prettier --check .`)
# then all agree. Without this, a git-for-windows default checkout (autocrlf=true)
# gives a CRLF working tree and `prettier --check` false-fails on a clean tree. (#6)
* text=auto eol=lf
